videos.description: Jonathan Williams takes the ball from half court, drives in the lane and hits the 2-point shot while falling backwards to the floor.
videos.headline: VCU's Williams sinks ridiculous falling layup

videos.description: Duncan Robinson takes the pass on the perimeter, fakes a 3-point shot, drives to the lane and puts the moves on for 2 points.
videos.headline: Michigan's Robinson with crafty layup

videos.description: Duncan Robinson pump fakes from three, then drives past defenders for the and-1 layup to extend Michigan's lead late in the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Robinson gets the and-1 with extra effort
